64 bytes from fd15:4ba5:5a2b:1009:20c:29ff:fef3:f848: icmp_seq=1 ttl=64 time=0.257 ms
64 bytes from fd15:4ba5:5a2b:1009:20c:29ff:fef3:f848: icmp_seq=2 ttl=64 time=0.421 ms</sentence>
        </paragraph>
